2:T734,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Lingvanex better than Smartling?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Lingvanex scores 5.0 overall while Smartling scores 8.0. Lingvanex is best for privacy-conscious organizations and on-premise needs, while Smartling excels for enterprise localization and SaaS companies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Lingvanex or Smartling?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Lingvanex starts at Free and Smartling starts at Custom. Lingvanex offers a free plan.  Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Lingvanex to Smartling?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Lingvanex and Smartling support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Lingvanex vs Smartling?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Lingvanex holds an overall rating of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Smartling has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Lingvanex for on-premise deployment option and Smartling for excellent enterprise tms platform."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Lingvanex or Smartling?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Smartling for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Lingvanex remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize on-premise deployment option. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"_